WEBVTT

00:00:04.839 --> 00:00:10.052
Is the destiny of mankind controlled
by some transcendental entity or Law?

00:00:10.928 --> 00:00:13.931
Is it like the hand of
God hovering above?

00:00:15.016 --> 00:00:16.767
At least it is true...

00:00:17.268 --> 00:00:20.896
...that man has no
control, even over his own will.

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:28.074
Watch Online Movies and Series for FREE
www.osdb.link/lm

00:00:34.285 --> 00:00:35.453
What the hell happened?

00:01:05.816 --> 00:01:07.818
<i>Feel no shame about shape.</i>

00:01:08.027 --> 00:01:09.820
<i>Weather changes the phrase.</i>

00:01:09.945 --> 00:01:13.449
<i>Even mother will
show you another way.</i>

00:01:13.699 --> 00:01:15.910
<i>So, put your glasses on.</i>

00:01:16.035 --> 00:01:17.953
<i>Nothing will be wrong.</i>

00:01:18.079 --> 00:01:20.206
<i>There's no blame, there's no fame.</i>

00:01:20.331 --> 00:01:22.041
<i>It's up to you.</i>

00:01:22.208 --> 00:01:25.669
<i>The first words should be found.</i>

00:01:26.337 --> 00:01:29.298
<i>Whatever holds you back.</i>

00:01:30.091 --> 00:01:30.674
<i>I...</i>

00:01:31.092 --> 00:01:31.801
<i>... can...</i>

00:01:31.926 --> 00:01:33.969
<i>I can get it off.</i>

00:01:34.095 --> 00:01:34.970
<i>Tell me what...</i>

00:01:35.221 --> 00:01:35.971
<i>Tell me what...</i>

00:01:36.097 --> 00:01:37.807
<i>Tell me what you want.</i>

00:01:37.973 --> 00:01:38.974
<i>I don't know why...</i>

00:01:39.183 --> 00:01:39.934
<i>I don't know why...</i>

00:01:40.059 --> 00:01:41.852
<i>I don't know why you are afraid.</i>

00:01:42.103 --> 00:01:43.062
<i>Tell me what...</i>

00:01:43.229 --> 00:01:43.979
<i>Tell me what...</i>

00:01:44.230 --> 00:01:45.689
<i>Tell me what you'd say.</i>

00:01:45.981 --> 00:01:46.982
<i>I don't know why...</i>

00:01:47.191 --> 00:01:48.109
<i>I don't know why...</i>

00:01:48.234 --> 00:01:48.859
<i>Too late...</i>

00:01:49.068 --> 00:01:50.569
<i>It's too late.</i>

00:01:55.616 --> 00:01:59.620
The Great Eclipse

00:02:09.255 --> 00:02:10.172
What is this?

00:02:10.256 --> 00:02:11.799
Where the hell are we?

00:02:12.049 --> 00:02:12.800
Hey!

00:02:12.925 --> 00:02:16.262
Weren't we just riding
over the grassy plains?

00:02:16.554 --> 00:02:19.890
Or were we just
dreaming as we rode along?

00:02:20.391 --> 00:02:23.394
Or without realizing it...

00:02:23.561 --> 00:02:25.813
...d- d-did we all just die?

00:02:26.147 --> 00:02:27.064
Calm down!

00:02:27.189 --> 00:02:28.190
Calm down?

00:02:28.315 --> 00:02:30.442
How the hell are we
going to calm down?

00:02:30.693 --> 00:02:31.402
Quiet!

00:02:33.445 --> 00:02:34.572
Everyone, compose yourselves!

00:02:34.947 --> 00:02:36.699
Forget about what
you can't understand!

00:02:37.158 --> 00:02:38.576
Focus on what you can do!

00:02:39.034 --> 00:02:40.786
Everyone, make a tight formation!

00:02:41.036 --> 00:02:42.538
No one is to stray from the group!

00:02:42.830 --> 00:02:44.582
Guts, get Griffith on your horse!

00:02:44.707 --> 00:02:45.583
Got it!

00:02:47.835 --> 00:02:49.712
Hurry up, over there!

00:02:50.588 --> 00:02:52.339
Under these circumstances...

00:02:52.673 --> 00:02:54.425
She's one hell of a woman.

00:02:55.092 --> 00:02:56.802
All right Griffith, here we go.

00:02:59.305 --> 00:03:01.557
What is this doing here?

00:03:02.349 --> 00:03:05.936
I know for sure Griffith didn't
have this when we rescued him.

00:03:07.605 --> 00:03:09.481
This strange shape...

00:03:15.821 --> 00:03:16.739
Griffith.

00:03:17.823 --> 00:03:19.742
The time has come...

00:03:20.326 --> 00:03:23.621
Time for the midnight festival...

00:03:25.706 --> 00:03:30.753
The banquet that
happens only once in 216 years...

00:03:31.086 --> 00:03:33.005
The Great Eclipse!

00:03:33.505 --> 00:03:34.882
Where did they come from...

00:03:35.591 --> 00:03:37.635
What the hell are they?

00:03:38.135 --> 00:03:39.511
He is coming...

00:03:39.637 --> 00:03:41.847
His presence is imminent...

00:03:42.014 --> 00:03:45.142
The King of the supreme beings...

00:03:45.517 --> 00:03:49.647
It is the advent of
the four guardian angels!

00:04:38.153 --> 00:04:39.154
What the...

00:04:39.280 --> 00:04:40.656
What is it?

00:04:41.031 --> 00:04:42.241
A giant?

00:05:17.318 --> 00:05:19.069
One after the other...

00:05:19.320 --> 00:05:20.195
I'm dreaming...

00:05:20.321 --> 00:05:21.947
This has to be a dream!

00:05:23.532 --> 00:05:24.950
What next?

00:06:07.242 --> 00:06:08.994
What the hell is going on?

00:06:09.703 --> 00:06:12.498
It is time for the blessing.

00:06:13.999 --> 00:06:16.251
Welcome to this final chapter...

00:06:16.502 --> 00:06:19.254
The final destination...

00:06:20.506 --> 00:06:24.885
...for you, our sacred baby lambs.

00:06:25.386 --> 00:06:30.015
Enjoy this holy banquet to the fullest.

00:06:32.142 --> 00:06:34.269
Chosen by fate...

00:06:34.395 --> 00:06:35.896
Our Apostle, our Hawk!

00:06:36.105 --> 00:06:38.023
You are the appointed one.

00:06:38.899 --> 00:06:41.485
Here in this place, in this moment...

00:06:41.985 --> 00:06:45.656
You who have been
chosen by the hand of God.

00:06:46.115 --> 00:06:48.242
We are your kinsmen...

00:06:48.367 --> 00:06:50.661
And presently,
you'll be our blessed King!

00:06:56.166 --> 00:06:57.042
Griffith?

00:06:57.668 --> 00:06:59.002
Kinsmen?

00:06:59.753 --> 00:07:01.046
Griffith is a...

00:07:03.006 --> 00:07:04.425
Cut the crap!

00:07:04.675 --> 00:07:08.053
You drag us into this God forsaken
place and on top of that you think...

00:07:08.178 --> 00:07:09.888
...you can say
whatever the hell you want!

00:07:10.514 --> 00:07:11.682
Apostle?

00:07:11.807 --> 00:07:12.683
Kinsmen?

00:07:13.058 --> 00:07:14.435
Don't be ridiculous!

00:07:14.560 --> 00:07:17.771
There's not one shred of him
that resembles the likes of you!

00:07:17.896 --> 00:07:20.315
Don't you dare put him in
the same boat as you freaks!

00:07:20.691 --> 00:07:21.442
Guts!

00:07:29.074 --> 00:07:31.410
What a beautiful friendship.

00:07:31.827 --> 00:07:36.540
You will certainly be an
excellent sacrificial offering...

00:07:36.957 --> 00:07:38.041
A sacrifice?

00:07:40.461 --> 00:07:41.211
Yes.

00:07:41.587 --> 00:07:44.965
The precious sacrifice that is
necessary for him to become a demon.

00:07:45.466 --> 00:07:46.550
Demon...

00:07:46.842 --> 00:07:47.968
Sacrifice?

00:07:48.469 --> 00:07:49.845
Exactly.

00:07:49.970 --> 00:07:54.099
From the moment you took
hold of the Crimson Behelit...

00:07:54.558 --> 00:07:58.103
You were qualified to become a demon.

00:07:59.188 --> 00:08:02.316
In fact, it is because
you inherently possessed...

00:08:02.441 --> 00:08:04.860
...the predestined
requirements that...

00:08:05.110 --> 00:08:06.820
...the Behelit fell into your hands.

00:08:06.987 --> 00:08:09.865
And the fact you used
the Behelit to summon us...

00:08:10.073 --> 00:08:13.869
...is proof that you are
qualified to become one of us.

00:08:14.244 --> 00:08:19.208
All the corpses that have
gathered here have used Behelits...

00:08:19.249 --> 00:08:23.003
...to take on the form
they were destined to assume.

00:08:23.504 --> 00:08:25.088
You don't mean that...

00:08:26.840 --> 00:08:28.342
So all the demons really are...

00:08:28.884 --> 00:08:33.764
And the Behelit you hold in
your hand is no ordinary Behelit!

00:08:34.181 --> 00:08:36.058
The crimson Behelit falls...

00:08:36.141 --> 00:08:39.895
...only into the hands of us guardian
angels, those destined to become...

00:08:40.062 --> 00:08:41.438
...members of the God Hand.

00:08:42.648 --> 00:08:44.316
The Egg of the King.

00:08:47.319 --> 00:08:50.447
And all of you are here to
serve as sacrificial offerings...

00:08:50.948 --> 00:08:53.450
...for the christening of this angel...

00:09:28.360 --> 00:09:32.739
You're saying that you will
transform Griffith into one of these beasts?

00:09:33.115 --> 00:09:35.200
In exchange for our lives?

00:09:35.492 --> 00:09:37.452
Not quite.

00:09:37.744 --> 00:09:39.454
It will be his will, not ours.

00:09:39.997 --> 00:09:42.833
It is he who will
offer you as sacrifices...

00:09:47.129 --> 00:09:48.839
That's impossible...

00:09:49.256 --> 00:09:50.382
It's impossible.

00:09:50.841 --> 00:09:53.844
It is all fixed in the flow of destiny...

00:09:54.595 --> 00:09:56.888
When his fate was fixed long ago...

00:09:57.014 --> 00:09:59.975
...your lives were spun
in to the web of his destiny...

00:10:00.100 --> 00:10:03.395
...by being chosen as the
sacrificial offerings for this final moment.

00:10:03.770 --> 00:10:06.523
We will now begin
the Baptism ceremony.

00:10:06.648 --> 00:10:08.525
Bring him to the altar!

00:10:12.029 --> 00:10:12.988
What the...

00:10:27.294 --> 00:10:28.253
Guts!

00:10:28.378 --> 00:10:29.421
Griffith!

00:11:18.970 --> 00:11:20.472
Baptism!

00:11:20.847 --> 00:11:21.848
Baptism!

00:11:22.432 --> 00:11:23.850
Baptism!

00:11:24.184 --> 00:11:25.602
Baptism!

00:11:25.727 --> 00:11:26.812
Baptism!

00:11:41.493 --> 00:11:43.245
Are you afraid?

00:11:43.453 --> 00:11:44.871
Of us?

00:11:45.580 --> 00:11:48.625
Of those who are
infinitely more powerful than you?

00:11:48.750 --> 00:11:51.211
Of our almighty power?

00:11:51.628 --> 00:11:52.879
Or is it the future?

00:11:53.463 --> 00:11:57.259
Before we venture in to the
future, let us venture back once more...

00:11:57.718 --> 00:12:00.095
...to the landscape of your past...

00:12:00.262 --> 00:12:02.139
You shall know the truth.

00:12:02.389 --> 00:12:05.016
And see exactly what it is you are...

00:12:09.980 --> 00:12:10.772
What?

00:12:11.398 --> 00:12:13.650
Did everyone go home?

00:12:14.276 --> 00:12:17.028
We all said we were
going to see the castle.

00:12:18.530 --> 00:12:19.531
Oh Well...

00:12:19.740 --> 00:12:20.782
I'll go by myself.

00:12:30.125 --> 00:12:32.502
Hey, where am I?

00:12:32.753 --> 00:12:33.920
I think I'm lost.

00:12:34.629 --> 00:12:35.797
Hey, old lady.

00:12:36.047 --> 00:12:37.299
Which way is the castle?

00:12:40.051 --> 00:12:41.052
This way?

00:12:42.429 --> 00:12:43.430
Thank you.

00:12:44.306 --> 00:12:45.557
Yes, yes.

00:12:45.807 --> 00:12:49.269
Your friends went
ahead, they'll be waiting.

00:13:05.285 --> 00:13:08.413
I think I've ended up
somewhere I shouldn't be.

00:13:09.206 --> 00:13:10.957
Hey, anybody there?

00:13:24.554 --> 00:13:26.932
You are a noisy child!

00:13:27.724 --> 00:13:29.684
Old lady, it's horrible!

00:13:30.101 --> 00:13:31.978
There are so many dead people...

00:13:32.103 --> 00:13:32.938
I know...

00:13:33.313 --> 00:13:34.731
You know?

00:13:34.815 --> 00:13:36.817
That's terrible,
you knew and you lied to me.

00:13:37.067 --> 00:13:38.485
I didn't lie.

00:13:39.110 --> 00:13:42.614
This is the only path
that leads to the castle.

00:13:42.989 --> 00:13:43.949
The only path...

00:13:44.366 --> 00:13:49.621
Those who are heading towards the
castle must either step over those who...

00:13:49.830 --> 00:13:53.875
...have fallen, or become
one of them and remain here.

00:13:54.376 --> 00:13:57.379
See here, it's your friend!

00:14:03.885 --> 00:14:05.262
Y-You're...

00:14:06.221 --> 00:14:09.766
You're going to the castle
to become King, aren't you?

00:14:10.141 --> 00:14:11.393
You're amazing!

00:14:12.018 --> 00:14:14.145
I want to be a knight one day...

00:14:14.396 --> 00:14:15.021
See?

00:14:16.022 --> 00:14:16.773
Hey...

00:14:17.774 --> 00:14:19.901
Take me with you.

00:14:20.026 --> 00:14:21.528
I'll give you this if you do.

00:14:22.279 --> 00:14:24.656
I'll work hard, I promise.

00:14:25.031 --> 00:14:26.116
All right?

00:14:27.367 --> 00:14:28.410
No...

00:14:28.660 --> 00:14:29.244
What?

00:14:29.369 --> 00:14:30.370
Why not?

00:14:31.413 --> 00:14:32.414
No, I can't...

00:14:32.789 --> 00:14:35.500
Because you're already...

00:14:37.168 --> 00:14:39.004
You're already dead...

00:14:39.379 --> 00:14:42.173
Take us with you too...

00:14:42.507 --> 00:14:44.926
We want to fight with you...

00:14:45.427 --> 00:14:48.013
I believe you can
make it to the castle...

00:14:48.430 --> 00:14:51.308
I would love to see
the empire you'll build...

00:14:51.808 --> 00:14:55.061
I want to fight under your flag...

00:14:55.937 --> 00:14:56.813
No...

00:14:57.188 --> 00:14:58.189
You can't...

00:14:58.315 --> 00:14:59.566
I can't take you with me...

00:15:00.025 --> 00:15:01.818
You're all dead...

00:15:02.152 --> 00:15:04.029
None of you are alive anymore!

00:15:04.321 --> 00:15:08.283
That's why I can't take
any of you to the castle!

00:15:10.535 --> 00:15:12.954
I'm sorry, I'm so sorry...

00:15:13.288 --> 00:15:15.707
Well, well, what a child you are.

00:15:16.291 --> 00:15:20.462
You must know that it's your fault
that these people ended up this way.

00:15:21.212 --> 00:15:22.714
Isn't that so?

00:15:22.839 --> 00:15:25.717
It is by following your lead
that they ended up this way...

00:15:25.842 --> 00:15:28.595
If you hadn't said that
you wanted to venture up there...

00:15:28.720 --> 00:15:31.222
...then none of this
would have happened.

00:15:31.806 --> 00:15:32.974
But...

00:15:33.350 --> 00:15:35.852
I never forced anyone to come along...

00:15:36.102 --> 00:15:38.355
Oh, what a thing to say!

00:15:38.480 --> 00:15:42.317
How do you think you
were able to come thus far?

00:15:42.943 --> 00:15:43.985
Listen now!

00:15:44.110 --> 00:15:45.820
The cobblestones that pave this path...

00:15:45.946 --> 00:15:48.865
...you have taken are
made from dead bodies.

00:15:49.324 --> 00:15:50.825
And that's not all.

00:15:50.951 --> 00:15:54.079
Those people have laid three,
four, five fold more cobble stones...

00:15:54.204 --> 00:15:55.830
...with bodies of others they killed...

00:15:55.956 --> 00:15:58.333
...so that you could
get to where you are now.

00:15:59.250 --> 00:16:01.086
There, take a look...

00:16:01.628 --> 00:16:05.006
If you are to make it
all the way to the castle...

00:16:05.131 --> 00:16:09.010
...you will need to pave your
path with many more stones...

00:16:10.470 --> 00:16:11.388
What's wrong?

00:16:11.513 --> 00:16:13.223
Are you scared now?

00:16:13.723 --> 00:16:15.976
Do you want to turn back now?

00:16:16.518 --> 00:16:18.645
You can't think like that!

00:16:19.020 --> 00:16:21.106
If you let your fears conquer you...

00:16:21.231 --> 00:16:23.900
...you will become just like
one of these cobblestones.

00:16:26.152 --> 00:16:29.280
Look closely now at your own hands.

00:16:34.285 --> 00:16:35.745
My hands!

00:16:36.037 --> 00:16:37.664
What a silly boy!

00:16:38.373 --> 00:16:40.542
If you were going to end
up regretting your actions...

00:16:40.667 --> 00:16:42.669
...you should have never
come here in the first place.

00:16:43.044 --> 00:16:45.880
This is not such a soft place!

00:16:47.007 --> 00:16:52.178
Why couldn't you be satisfied by simply
gazing at the castle from an alleyway?

00:16:58.059 --> 00:16:59.310
I...

00:16:59.686 --> 00:17:01.396
I didn't know...

00:17:01.646 --> 00:17:02.772
Be quiet!

00:17:02.897 --> 00:17:05.984
You must have known
what kind of place this was!

00:17:11.656 --> 00:17:12.907
Known...

00:17:13.158 --> 00:17:14.284
...all along...

00:17:14.784 --> 00:17:16.661
...and walked all over them...

00:17:17.412 --> 00:17:18.496
...to get here...

00:17:20.248 --> 00:17:22.000
What are you saying now?

00:17:25.170 --> 00:17:28.298
This is the path that
leads to your dream, isn't it?

00:17:29.174 --> 00:17:30.759
That's what you believe, right?

00:17:31.384 --> 00:17:33.511
Why are you stalling
after all that's happened?

00:17:34.804 --> 00:17:36.681
That's right, now go lay those stones.

00:17:36.931 --> 00:17:38.516
It's not too late.

00:17:38.808 --> 00:17:40.935
You have no other choice!

00:17:41.269 --> 00:17:45.440
Before you become one of
them, lay those cobblestones!

00:17:50.278 --> 00:17:50.904
Yes.

00:17:53.031 --> 00:17:55.075
What is the point
of regretting anything?

00:17:56.034 --> 00:17:58.036
What's the use in repenting my sins?

00:18:00.538 --> 00:18:02.665
What can I possibly
say to those who have died?

00:18:03.833 --> 00:18:05.919
I cannot apologize to them now.

00:18:06.836 --> 00:18:07.837
This is...

00:18:08.588 --> 00:18:11.299
...the path that I have chosen.

00:18:11.591 --> 00:18:16.971
If I regret my actions or
apologize for them, then it's all over.

00:18:18.181 --> 00:18:22.060
And I will never
reach my destined goal...

00:18:23.937 --> 00:18:24.979
Yes.

00:18:25.105 --> 00:18:27.482
That is who you are.

00:18:28.983 --> 00:18:30.110
An illusion?

00:18:30.318 --> 00:18:32.112
Not an illusion.

00:18:32.237 --> 00:18:35.115
It is the reality in your consciousness.

00:18:35.698 --> 00:18:37.242
Reaching for the
castle in the heavens...

00:18:37.367 --> 00:18:41.121
Stacking cobblestones to the
highest summit, that is your destiny.

00:18:42.122 --> 00:18:44.457
You have come thus far...

00:18:44.624 --> 00:18:48.837
Stepping over the thousands
of stones that are your brothers...

00:18:49.212 --> 00:18:52.132
...and the tens of thousands
of stones they paved for you.

00:18:52.257 --> 00:18:54.217
Disregarding what or who they were...

00:18:54.634 --> 00:18:57.011
You carried only
one thought in your mind...

00:18:57.887 --> 00:19:01.975
And now you have
reached the end of the path.

00:19:02.851 --> 00:19:04.144
Look around...

00:19:05.645 --> 00:19:09.858
The gift at the final
destination of your bloody journey.

00:19:10.900 --> 00:19:13.778
All the wings that carried
you above your comrades...

00:19:13.903 --> 00:19:15.530
Each pair of wings...

00:19:16.114 --> 00:19:18.283
Surely they will forgive you...

00:19:19.242 --> 00:19:22.412
Although they imagine
they have fallen into despair...

00:19:22.537 --> 00:19:25.540
They will welcome
you with open arms...

00:19:26.624 --> 00:19:29.419
And you shall live on...

00:19:29.878 --> 00:19:32.255
Entrust your
wounded soul with them...

00:19:33.298 --> 00:19:35.550
Leave your past behind...

00:19:36.759 --> 00:19:39.387
And bury yourself in
the debris of your dreams.

00:19:41.681 --> 00:19:42.765
The debris...

00:19:43.183 --> 00:19:44.434
...of my dreams...

00:19:44.559 --> 00:19:48.938
That is the punishment of God.

00:19:50.773 --> 00:19:53.026
But if your dream is still alive...

00:19:53.651 --> 00:19:58.031
If that castle still gleams in your eyes...

00:19:58.448 --> 00:20:02.952
You must stack the
remaining stones that surround you...

00:20:03.578 --> 00:20:05.413
Let us chant...

00:20:05.788 --> 00:20:07.081
This we offer!

00:20:08.082 --> 00:20:12.462
Hesitation will not grant the black wings
to fly from the mountain tops to the heavens.

00:20:14.088 --> 00:20:16.591
Fate frees one from human reasoning...

00:20:16.716 --> 00:20:20.428
If reason sees children only as
toys, then by the Laws of Karma...

00:20:20.553 --> 00:20:23.473
...a child must embrace
the evil within and face fate!

00:20:23.932 --> 00:20:24.849
Griffith!

00:20:37.111 --> 00:20:38.196
Yes...

00:20:38.738 --> 00:20:43.117
Out of all the thousands of comrades
and tens of thousands of enemies.

00:20:43.576 --> 00:20:44.869
Only one...

00:20:46.496 --> 00:20:48.873
You and you alone...

00:20:54.629 --> 00:20:56.965
You allowed me to forget my dream...

00:20:58.841 --> 00:21:00.969
I offer myself.

00:21:07.850 --> 00:21:09.143
Griffith.

00:21:09.477 --> 00:21:14.148
The threads of destiny
are now bound together...

00:21:14.399 --> 00:21:16.776
The promised time has come!

00:22:03.031 --> 00:22:05.158
<i>Looking back, the morning comes.</i>

00:22:05.283 --> 00:22:08.828
<i>Don't find your face in your glass.</i>

00:22:10.038 --> 00:22:12.832
<i>Take the moonlight by the tail.</i>

00:22:12.957 --> 00:22:15.793
<i>It's a rainy sight that you're shading.</i>

00:22:17.545 --> 00:22:19.088
<i>What is that?</i>

00:22:19.213 --> 00:22:20.340
<i>It's just the same.</i>

00:22:20.465 --> 00:22:23.468
<i>What is trying on your crown?</i>

00:22:24.719 --> 00:22:27.680
<i>I'm spending my
glass and walking back.</i>

00:22:27.805 --> 00:22:30.975
<i>So wear my glass, you're fading.</i>

00:22:31.351 --> 00:22:34.604
<i>I'm waiting so long.</i>

00:22:35.104 --> 00:22:37.982
<i>I'm waiting so long.</i>

00:22:38.691 --> 00:22:41.736
<i>I'm waiting so long.</i>

00:22:42.612 --> 00:22:45.365
<i>I'm waiting...</i>

00:23:06.886 --> 00:23:08.888
Next Episode

00:23:33.913 --> 00:23:36.916
Time of Eternity

